# 🚛 Swift Haulage Logistics System – BTS4723 Project

This repository contains the **Functional and Non-Functional Requirements** and supporting documents for the proposed logistics and fleet management system designed for **Swift Haulage Berhad**. The system aims to automate trucking operations, enhance real-time tracking, optimize delivery routes, and improve overall logistics performance.

