## 📘 Glossary

| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| **ETA** | Estimated Time of Arrival |
| **ePOD** | Electronic Proof of Delivery |
| **LHDN** | Inland Revenue Board of Malaysia |
| **PDPA** | Personal Data Protection Act |
| **GDPR** | General Data Protection Regulation |

---

## 🧍‍♂️ User Stories

- As a **Driver**, I want to log fuel usage, so I can track my consumption easily.  
- As a **Dispatcher**, I want to assign available trucks automatically, so I can reduce delays.  
- As a **Customer**, I want to view my delivery history and live status, so I can track my orders.  
- As a **Manager**, I want to receive delay notifications, so I can respond quickly to disruptions.

